  "texts": [
    "Through the aid of CAD techniques, early detection of AD has today become more efficient and robust.",
    "Advancements in neuroimaging techniques like positron emission tomography (PET) and magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) scans, coupled with new machine learning (ML) techniques have contributed to the CAD methods (Ghazal and Issa 2022).",
    "Several diagnostic datasets are now available across various sources like open access series of imaging studies (OASIS) and Alzheimer's disease neuroimaging initiative (ADNI) that include patient health records such as demographic, imaging, clinical, and genetic details, etc.",
    "These datasets are today being used by researchers, academicians, and industrialists to develop ML techniques for CAD (El-Sappagh et al. 2021a).",
    "In the past, several surveys have been published on CAD of the AD."
  ],
